column4: NSLOCTEXT("[BD5EE5BF4A774B80563B02852DAA6883]", "204DF12F4E76BC666BB01B81E84B32A0", "I record Jijimon\'s info and give it to you.")
NSLOCTEXT("[BD5EE5BF4A774B80563B02852DAA6883]", "74B75C9B4AEC2FF7BA7D429AC982A2D4", "If you don\'t know what to do ask me, and I\'ll tell you where to go.")
NSLOCTEXT("[BD5EE5BF4A774B80563B02852DAA6883]", "F5C24F7D46FC386458499D907C52832F", "Let me tell you what I know. Let\'s see...")
